@page "/privacy-policy"

<PageTitle>Privacy Policy - Learn It All</PageTitle>

<div class="page-container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="form-hint">Last updated: July 2026</p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you create an account, we collect your first name, last name, phone number, and email address through Microsoft Entra External ID. Your email is provided by the sign-in provider you choose (Google, Facebook, or Microsoft); other details are entered by you during account setup.</p>

    <h2>Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
    <p>We use your browser's local storage to remember your theme preference and to keep you signed in between visits. We also show ads through Google AdSense, which may set cookies to personalize the ads you see. You can review and manage how Google uses this data at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.</p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your account information is used to verify your identity, manage your purchased book library, and let you read the books you own. We do not sell your personal information.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>This app uses Microsoft Entra External ID for authentication (with Google, Facebook, and Microsoft as sign-in options) and Google AdSense for advertising. Each of these providers has its own privacy policy governing how they handle data.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about this policy can be sent to <a href="mailto:learn.it.all.41@gmail.com">learn.it.all.41@gmail.com</a>.</p>
</div>
